[59-59] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[60-119] "                                                            " fg=def bg=#121212
--row 2--
[0-0] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[1-56] "Fear is the little-death that brings total obliteration." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#00008b
[57-58] "  " fg=def bg=#00008b
[59-59] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[60-119] "                                                            " fg=def bg=#121212
--row 3--
[0-0] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[1-20] "I will face my fear." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#00008b
[21-58] "                                      " fg=def bg=#00008b
[59-59] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[60-119] "                                                            " fg=def bg=#121212
--row 4--
[0-0] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[1-48] "I will permit it to pass over me and through me." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#00008b
[49-58] "          " fg=def bg=#00008b
[59-59] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[60-119] "                                                            " fg=def bg=#121212
--row 5--
[0-0] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[1-55] "And when it has gone past, I will turn the inner eye to" fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#00008b
[56-58] "   " fg=def bg=#00008b
[59-59] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[60-119] "                                                            " fg=def bg=#121212
--row 6--
[0-0] "┃" fg=#ffff00 bg=#00008b
[1-13] "see its path." fg=#e0e0e0 bg=#00008b
